bdd_gwgwebdriver

Enum How

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<How>
      • bdd_gwgwebdriver.How
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<How>

    public enum How
extends java.lang.Enum<How>
    How attribute defines the locator strategy for finding web elements.
    It supports both Selenium WebDriver original locators, but also Protrator locators.
